Template for default for jinja templates for reference datasets wirh --kins option:

# default: default date range for all analyses

# startdate, enddate: values for the date range for references to be used in the analysis
# std_startdate, std_enddate: standard deviation for references to be used in the analysis

default:
  default:
    startdate: "1990-01-01"
    enddate: "2014-12-31"
    std_startdate: "1990-01-01"
    std_enddate: "2014-12-31"
